name: #Sinkholesatori :01
description:
Sinkhole Satori is about... oh well it's about nothing really. I thought I heard somebody say it in a conversation, which they didn't but the same time I liked the way the words went together sinkhole and satori a bit like cellar door like in the film Donnie Darko.

In philosophy holes are very important to describe the void, the depths, the nothingness and in this space true enlightenment can be found.

Sinkhole Satori is the first is a series around this theme.
